              <history-note id="DLM2248845"><amended-provision>Schedule 1 clause 7(3)</amended-provision>: <amending-operation>amended</amending-operation>, on <amendment-date>25 January 2005</amendment-date>, by <amending-provision href="DLM331111">section 200</amending-provision> of the <amending-leg>Crown Entities Act 2004</amending-leg> (2004 No 115).</history-note>
